window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>What happens when a beast of blood finds a bride of light in the land of death?</b></p> <p>Growing up on the streets of Los Fortis, Alessandro 'Alpha' Villanova scrapped his way to the top, fighting for his very survival, losing everything in the process. The city that shunned him then is the one he rules now, albeit alone, as the king of a dark empire few know about.</p> <p>Far from Alpha's world, Zephyr de la Vega has a normal life, a normal family, and normal drama. Her biggest problem is people trying to make her lose a few pounds. When a chance encounter puts her on Alpha's path, she makes a proposition that changes the course of both their lives.</p> <p>As a killer goes on a spree in Alpha's city, taking apart his scarred empire corpse by corpse, and the Syndicate comes into play, Alpha and Zephyr's partnership evolves into something deeper, more enduring, and more powerful than either of them anticipated.</p> <p>Evil ascends. Darkness descends.</p> <p>A new order is born.</p> <p><i>The Finisher </i>is the highly anticipated fourth book in the Dark Verse series.It is not a standalone. Listening to the series in order is highly recommended.</p> <p>Cover design by Nelly R.</p>"; 
